query:
SELECT 
  rl.id,
  rl.customerId,
  rl.vehicleId,
  rl.messageType,
  rl.status,
  rl.sentAt,
  v.registration,
  c.name as customer_name,
  c.phone
FROM reminderLogs rl
LEFT JOIN vehicles v ON rl.vehicleId = v.id
LEFT JOIN customers c ON rl.customerId = c.id
WHERE rl.sentAt >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
ORDER BY rl.sentAt DESC
LIMIT 20;
